Ok not really, but I'm hoping for at least 10 more levels. I really don't see how Verant got out of increasing the levels for so long.  Sure its not an easy thing to add, but I think it hurt the game not to. They used messy quick fix ways of advancement in previous expansions, that just made EQ look like a patchwork game, but it somehow kept people playing.  They need to add real player advancement back into eq for those that have been stuck at level 60 for years.<br>
<br>
Of course thats just my opinion and I could be wrong.<br>
